des: Celebrate special occasions with your loved ones at our waterfront vacation rental in Provincetown. When you open the skill, Alexa will play a slideshow with rich images and audio. It will also provide you with our phone number (339.227.8427) and our direct booking website (www.ptown.bookingturbo.com). You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
